narratives.question_text: What knowledge, skills, and insights did you develop by taking this course?
comments: I deepened my understanding of Vietnamese. I learned more vocab and learned how to give thorough presentations in Vietnamese.

narratives.question_text: What are the strengths and weaknesses of this course and how could it be improved?
comments: The strengths is that there is a lot to learn and you do learn new vocab on various subjects. The weakness is that it moves fast. There was a vocab quiz or presentation assigned like 2 days after receiving new vocab, which does not always help you retain the language.

narratives.question_text: Would you recommend this course to another student? Please explain.
comments: Yes I would. L3 and L4 are much more challenging and so I found L5 to be a relaxed atmosphere to continue building my language skills.
